### Google Calendar Clone — REST API Demo
### Compatible with VS Code REST Client extension and JetBrains HTTP Client.
### Set @baseUrl before running.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HEALTH
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health


# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# LIST EVENTS (with RRULE expansion)
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get all events overlapping the week of 2026-06-28
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events?start=2026-06-28T00:00:00.000Z&end=2026-07-05T00:00:00.000Z&tz=America/New_York


# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CREATE — standalone event
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create a standalone one-off event
# @name standaloneEvent
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Team Lunch",
  "description": "Monthly team lunch at the usual spot",
  "location": "123 Main St",
  "colorId": "tomato",
  "startUtc": "2026-06-30T17:00:00.000Z",
  "endUtc": "2026-06-30T18:30:00.000Z",
  "isAllDay": false,
  "timezone": "America/New_York"
}


# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CREATE — recurring event
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create a weekly recurring event (Mon/Wed/Fri standup)
# @name recurringEvent
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Daily Standup",
  "colorId": "sage",
  "startUtc": "2026-06-29T14:00:00.000Z",
  "endUtc": "2026-06-29T14:15:00.000Z",
  "isAllDay": false,
  "timezone": "America/New_York",
  "rrule": "FREQ=WEEKLY;BYDAY=MO,WE,FR"
}

### Create an all-day recurring event (birthday, every year)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Sarah's Birthday",
  "colorId": "flamingo",
  "startUtc": "2026-07-04T00:00:00.000Z",
  "endUtc": "2026-07-04T23:59:59.000Z",
  "isAllDay": true,
  "timezone": "UTC",
  "rrule": "FREQ=YEARLY"
}


# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# UPDATE — edit all occurrences
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Edit ALL occurrences of a recurring event (rename + recolor)
### Replace <masterId> and <currentVersion> with values from the create response
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/events/<masterId>
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "version": 0,
  "editScope": "all",
  "title": "Standup (renamed)",
  "colorId": "banana"
}


# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# UPDATE — edit single occurrence (creates an override row)
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Edit only the Wednesday 2026-07-01 occurrence — move it 30 min later
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/events/<masterId>
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "version": 0,
  "editScope": "single",
  "originalStartUtc": "2026-07-01T14:00:00.000Z",
  "startUtc": "2026-07-01T14:30:00.000Z",
  "endUtc": "2026-07-01T14:45:00.000Z",
  "title": "Standup (moved)"
}


# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# UPDATE — this and following (splits the series)
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### From the 2026-07-06 occurrence onward, rename and change cadence to daily
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/events/<masterId>
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "version": 0,
  "editScope": "thisAndFollowing",
  "originalStartUtc": "2026-07-06T14:00:00.000Z",
  "title": "Daily Sync (new cadence)",
  "rrule": "FREQ=DAILY"
}


# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# UPDATE — optimistic concurrency conflict demo
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Sending a stale version → expect 409 Conflict
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/events/<masterId>
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "version": 0,
  "editScope": "all",
  "title": "This should 409 if version was already bumped"
}


# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# DELETE — single occurrence (writes EXDATE exception row)
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Cancel just the Friday 2026-07-03 standup
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/events/<masterId>
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "editScope": "single",
  "originalStartUtc": "2026-07-03T14:00:00.000Z"
}


# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# DELETE — this and following
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### End the series from 2026-08-01 onward (caps RRULE with UNTIL)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/events/<masterId>
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "editScope": "thisAndFollowing",
  "originalStartUtc": "2026-08-03T14:00:00.000Z"
}


# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# DELETE — entire series
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Delete the entire recurring event and all its exceptions/overrides
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/events/<masterId>
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "editScope": "all"
}

### Delete a standalone event (editScope defaults to "all")
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/events/<standaloneEventId>


# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# OVERLAP CHECK
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Check for events overlapping a proposed time slot
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events/check-overlap
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "startUtc": "2026-06-30T17:00:00.000Z",
  "endUtc": "2026-06-30T18:30:00.000Z"
}

### Same check but excluding the event being edited (so it doesn't conflict with itself)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events/check-overlap
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "startUtc": "2026-06-30T17:00:00.000Z",
  "endUtc": "2026-06-30T18:30:00.000Z",
  "excludeId": "<standaloneEventId>"
}


# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# VALIDATION ERROR DEMOS (expect 400)
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Missing required fields → 400 with details array
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "description": "No title, no times"
}

### endUtc before startUtc → 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Bad times",
  "startUtc": "2026-07-01T18:00:00.000Z",
  "endUtc": "2026-07-01T17:00:00.000Z",
  "timezone": "UTC"
}

### editScope single without originalStartUtc → 400
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/events/<masterId>
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "version": 0,
  "editScope": "single",
  "title": "Forgot originalStartUtc"
}
